        "prompt": "Create an original, non-infringing travel brochure design for a 4-day Hangzhou itinerary, featuring a real Hangzhou map as the main visual thread.\n\nStyle/medium: photorealistic product photography, tri-fold brochure mockup with die-cut landmarks floating above textured card stock, editorial travel guide aesthetic\nComposition: top-down flat lay of an open tri-fold brochure, each panel featuring a different day of the itinerary, famous scenic spots rendered as dimensional pop-up elements hovering 2-3mm above the paper surface\nSubject: tri-fold travel guide brochure for \"杭州市4天3晚\" with real Hangzhou map as background, iconic landmarks (西湖/Xihu, 断桥残雪, 雷峰塔, 灵隐寺, 龙井村, 九溪烟树, 西溪湿地) as raised cut-out elements with distinct architectural features\nScene/backdrop: clean kraft paper or cream-colored card stock surface, subtle shadow beneath floating elements, minimal desk environment\nLighting/mood: soft diffused overhead light from upper left, gentle shadows under floating landmarks, warm inviting mood suggesting premium travel planning\nColor palette: muted earth tones (kraft brown, cream) as base, vibrant green for tea fields and West Lake, warm terracotta for temples, clear blue for water features\nMaterials/textures: matte card stock with subtle fiber texture, glossy raised landmark cutouts with slight embossing, visible paper grain on map background\nText (verbatim): \"杭州市4天3晚\" / \"第一天：西湖经典游\" / \"断桥残雪→白堤→孤山→曲院风荷→苏堤春晓→花港观鱼→雷峰塔→柳浪闻莺\" / \"第二天：禅意杭州\" / \"灵隐寺→飞来峰造像→法喜寺→宋城\" / \"第三天：九溪烟树徒步\" / \"九溪十八涧→龙井村→十里琅珰→云栖竹径\" / \"第四天：文艺收官\" / \"运河文艺线\" / \"西溪湿地轻奢游\"\nConstraints: must clearly show three distinct folded panels; landmarks must be recognizable silhouettes; map must be geographically accurate Hangzhou layout; floating effect must be physically believable\nAvoid: generic stock photo aesthetic; plastic-looking pop-ups; cluttered composition; illegible tiny text; mismatched landmark styles; cartoonish illustrations; watermarks",
